<item>
            <title>[WICKET-4770] Wicket 6: modal windows in Safari are always in drag or resize mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4770</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Wicket 6 using Safari, a modal dialog will not allow interactions with form components. The whole dialog always seems to be in &quot;drag&quot; mode. Click anywhere on the panel and the dialog will drag.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Interaction works fine with all other browsers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Safari - all OS</environment>
        <key id="12608093">WICKET-4770</key>
            <summary>Wicket 6: modal windows in Safari are always in drag or resize mode</summary>
